# Copy to .env and fill in. Never commit the real .env (it is gitignored).
#
# Featherless.ai API key — powers the live courtroom judges (api/judge.ts)
# and the topic-submission gate (api/validate-prompt.ts).
# Without it the game still runs on cached mock verdicts.
# Get one at https://featherless.ai → API keys.
FEATHERLESS_API_KEY=your-key-here
